<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٧٠٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4779">عِمْرَانُ بْنُ مَيْسَرَةَ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5879">ابْنُ فُضَيْلٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1513">حُصَيْنٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3071">عَامِرٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4764">عِمْرَانَ بْنِ حُصَيْنٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَا رُقْيَةَ إِلَّا مِنْ عَيْنٍ أَوْ حُمَةٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>